Package: ffiec
Type: Package
Title: FFIEC Central Data Repository REST API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Michael", "Thomas", email = "mthomas@ketchbrookanalytics.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ketchbrook Analytics", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: A client for the FFIEC (Federal Financial Institutions Examination
    Council) Central Data Repository REST API. Provides functions to retrieve
    Reports of Condition and Income (Call Reports) and Uniform Bank Performance
    Reports (UBPRs) in list or tidy data frame format for most FDIC-insured
    institutions.
